headline: Gilead Announces New England Journal of Medicine Publication of PURPOSE 2 Results
summary: FOSTER CITY, Calif., November 27, 2024--Gilead Sciences, Inc. (Nasdaq: GILD) today announced The New England Journal of Medicine (NEJM) published the full results from the company’s pivotal Phase 3 PURPOSE 2 trial evaluating twice-yearly lenacapavir for the investigational use of HIV prevention among a broad and geographically diverse range of cisgender men and gender-diverse people.
